										<ECUC-STRING-PARAM-DEF UUID="fdca66d5-16da-4a62-8603-9223cde11dfc">
											<SHORT-NAME>CryptoVendorApiInfix</SHORT-NAME>
											<DESC>
												<L-2 L="EN">This parameter can be used to overwrite the "ModuleName", “Vendor-ID” and “API-Infix” attributes of the real component, if necessary.

Example:
In general the implementation specific API name is specified as:
&lt;ModuleName&gt;_&lt;vendorId&gt;_&lt;vendorApiInfix&gt;_&lt;API name from module&gt;

This parameter overwrites the whole parenthesis &lt;ModuleName&gt;_&lt;vendorId&gt;_&lt;vendorApiInfix&gt;.</L-2>
											</DESC>
											<LOWER-MULTIPLICITY>0</LOWER-MULTIPLICITY>
											<UPPER-MULTIPLICITY>1</UPPER-MULTIPLICITY>
											<IMPLEMENTATION-CONFIG-CLASSES>
												<ECUC-IMPLEMENTATION-CONFIGURATION-CLASS>
													<CONFIG-CLASS>PRE-COMPILE</CONFIG-CLASS>
													<CONFIG-VARIANT>VARIANT-PRE-COMPILE</CONFIG-VARIANT>
												</ECUC-IMPLEMENTATION-CONFIGURATION-CLASS>
											</IMPLEMENTATION-CONFIG-CLASSES>
											<ORIGIN>Vector Informatik</ORIGIN>
											<REQUIRES-INDEX>false</REQUIRES-INDEX>
											<SYMBOLIC-NAME-VALUE>false</SYMBOLIC-NAME-VALUE>
