											<SHORT-NAME>CryptoUseVStdLib</SHORT-NAME>
											<LONG-NAME>
												<L-4 L="EN">Use VStdLib</L-4>
											</LONG-NAME>
											<DESC>
												<L-2 L="EN">If enabled the VStdLib is used for copy and clear data operations. If there is no VStdLib, disable the switch to use the implementation of the Crypto.</L-2>
											</DESC>
