											<SHORT-NAME>CryptoKeyExchangePrimitves</SHORT-NAME>
											<DESC>
												<L-2 L="EN">Configuration of a Crypto Key Exchange Primitive. If there is an algorithm configured, key exchange is usable via Crypto_KeyExchangeCalcPubVal and Crypto_KeyExchangeCalcSecret API.</L-2>
